        <http://example.org/tennis/tournament/US_Open> ;
    ns3:evidenceText "He also became the first male teenager to win a major singles title since Pete Sampras won the 1990 US Open at age 19.[8]",
        "Pete Sampras, 14 Grand Slam winner and known for his excellent serve, never won the French Open – his best result being a semi-final in 1996." ;
