<http://example.org/tennis/player/Alexander_Zverev> a ns2:Player ;
    rdfs:label "Alexander Zverev" ;
    ns2:playedAgainst <http://example.org/tennis/player/Andrey_Rublev>,
        <http://example.org/tennis/player/Carlos_Alcaraz>,
        <http://example.org/tennis/player/Casper_Ruud>,
        <http://example.org/tennis/player/Frances_Tiafoe>,
        <http://example.org/tennis/player/Nikola_Miloje>,
        <http://example.org/tennis/player/Novak_Djokovic>,
        <http://example.org/tennis/player/Pablo_Carreno_Busta>,
        <http://example.org/tennis/player/Rafael_Nadal> ;
    ns2:won <http://example.org/tennis/tournament/Australian_Open>,
        <http://example.org/tennis/tournament/US_Open> ;
    ns3:evidenceText "\"Alexander Zverev Beats Carlos Alcaraz at the French Open\".",
        "- \"Alexander Zverev beats Rafael Nadal to reach Paris final\".",
        "A few weeks later they had their first major meeting in the French Open quarterfinals, where Zverev defeated Alcaraz in four sets.[245]",
        "At the 2020 Summer Olympics, Djokovic sought a gold medal, but lost to Alexander Zverev in the semifinals and to Pablo Carreño Busta in the bronze match.[253]",
        "He received wildcards at the Mexican Open, where he lost to eventual champion Alexander Zverev in the first round;[49] at the Barcelona Open, where he lost to Frances Tiafoe in the first round;[50] and at the Andalucía Open, where he defeated Nikola Miloje",
        "They had further high profile encounters in the quarterfinals of the 2023 US Open, won by Alcaraz, and the quarterfinals of the 2024 Australian Open, won by Zverev.",
        "Zverev won the next two sets in a pair of tiebreaks, but Alcaraz recovered in time to win the fifth set, proceeding to his maiden Australian Open final." ;
    ns3:sourceURL "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carlos_Alcaraz"^^xsd:anyURI,
        "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Novak_Djokovic"^^xsd:anyURI,
        "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rafael_Nadal"^^xsd:anyURI ;
    owl:sameAs <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q237176> .

